column3: Latest;China: According to information released by the Chongqing Municipal Health Committee
column4: there has been another confirmed case of COVID-19 from a person traveling from Cambodia.------The announcement said that at 04:00 on March 28
column5: Chongqing health officials reported the case
column6: which was one of three cases imported and detected that day.------According the source
column7: the patient flew from Cambodia to Chengdu on March 20
column8: and was isolated after arriving in Chongqing
column9: where they were then later diagnosed. No more details were given.------Imported cases from Cambodia were reported in ------Shanghai on March 26------ ------Guangdong on March 26 ------ and ------Gansu province on March 19------.
